The paper deals with convergence analysis of a detection algorithm in a massive multiuser MIMO system, which involves information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), signal processing (cs.SI), networking (cs.NI), and possibly computer vision (cs.MM) if the system involves image or video data.
